&INFO
 Ar2 test for vdW with WFCs
&END

&CPMD
  USE_CUFFT 
  FFT_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  FFT_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  USE_CUBLAS
  BLAS_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  BLAS_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
 MOLECULAR DYNAMICS BO
 initialize wavefunctions random
 RESTART WAVEFUNCTION density coordinates LATEST
 QUENCH ELECTRONS BO
 DIPOLE DYNAMICS SAMPLE WANNIER
  1
 MAXSTEP
   1
 MAXITER
  10
 PCG MINIMIZE
 odiis
   5
 GDIIS
   2 
 CONVERGENCE ORBITALS
  0.00001
 annealing ions
  0.995
 tempcontrol ions
  300.0 30.0
 TIMESTEP IONS
  20.670724
 TIMESTEP ELECTRONS
   4.0
 EMASS
 400.0D0
 STRUCTURE BONDS ANGLES
 VDW WANNIER
 TRAJECTORY SAMPLE XYZ
  1
 RESTFILES
  2
 COMPRESS READ WRITE
 CENTER MOLECULE
 WANNIER TYPE resta VANDERBILT
 WANNIER OPTIMIZATION SD jacobi
 WANNIER PARAMETER
  0.2  1.e-05  0.01  1000
 WANNIER REFERENCE
  0.0000  0.0000  0.0000
 wannier wfnout partial densitiy
  4
  1 2 3 4
 taskgroups
  2
 distribute linalg on
 distribute fnl on
 blocksize states
  2
&END

&VDW
 WANNIER CORRECTION
   VERSION
     2
   FRAGMENT BOND
     1.38
   TOLERANCE WANNIER
     5.0
   TOLERANCE REFERENCE
     1.0
   PRINT INFO FRAGMENT
